c: 64
v: 16
t: "So pay obedience to Allah as you could, and listen (to the Ordainments in Al-Kitab), and obey and spend (in accordance with the teachings in Allah’s Scripture); (that is) better for your ownselves. And whosoever is saved from the covetousness of his own Nafs, then those people: they (very ones are) those who have achieved success"